_ohc=xrt-LLbm3j8Q7kNvgFYXBfW&_nc_ht=scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCqjSiWCv17mQe7qm_g1z2mIdCW1Ih4CDpO76Q-TVbYPw&oe=671A4213"}, {"file_name": "20210525-014936.png", "id": "490029918982047", "uri": "https://scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982562_490029922315380_2472132374884165007_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=gIWuAPtfJtEQ7kNvgGhiYNe&_nc_ht=scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBN_VZv3lWefzDXjkmQX5a9ElTYKaMNjkZnd7m6VQidTg&oe=671A2C72"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "\u30b9\u30af\u30ea\u30fc\u30f3\u30b7\u30e7\u30c3\u30c8 2021-05-29 23.06.46.png", "id": "873940063188913", "uri": "https://scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974479_873940066522246_2661076465911733640_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rhEBao8joJ0Q7kNvgGjkmko&_nc_ht=scontent-xsp1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA2kjJXtT0P9VtOVtO0GC1XUkPs4qFlT7DB8ouAX1l_9Q&oe=671A3E1A"}, "display_name": "Playing VR with Girl Friend", "keywords": [], "long_description": "[Description]\nEnjoy the conversation with your girl friend!\nThis is a strategy game.\nPlace the units in the map using your hand.\nDestory the enemy's Base to win!\nDefeat the enemies before they destroy your Base.\n\n[How to Play]\nUse your hand or a controller to play!\nPress the button, pick up the units and release them in the map!\nThe left and right sticks allow you to move the user's position slightly.\n\n[Type of Units]\n-Base\nThis is the Base.\nBuild your Base stronger!!\n\n-Fighter\nA common flying unit.\nGround & Air Attack.\n\n-Factory\nA factory unit.\nIt generates cash.\n\n-Bomber\nA flying unit skilled for\nbombing and ground attack.\n\n-Tank\nAn anti-ground unit.\nAttacks with rapid fire.\n\n-Anti-aircraft Artillery\nA placement unit using missles.\nEffective to flying units.\n\n-Sheild\nA placement unit for defense.\nIt has high durability.\n", "short_description": "Let's play a VR video game with your girl friend!\nThis time it's a strategy game.\